<br>
All tradeskills require some sort of container for combinations.<br>
Brewing has to be done in a brew barrel (located in most cities).<br>
Baking can be done in either a spit (portable) or an oven (stationary). Some recipes need to be done in a mixing bowl which is made through pottery.<br>
Jewlcraft requires a jewler's kit (portable).<br>
Smithing needs to be done in a forge (Stationary) which can be found in most cities.<br>
Fletching needs to be done in a fletchers kit (portable).<br>
Tailoring can be done in either a sewing kit (portable) or a loom (stationary). <p>&quot;You call THAT A nuke?&quot;<br>
